VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT where\(\s*"[^"]*#\{|find_by_sql\(|connection\.execute\(
WHEN EXPR MISSING:where\s*\(\s*".*?",|sanitize_sql|Arel::Nodes
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects raw/dynamic SQL construction patterns in Ruby frameworks.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Sinatra SQL Injection Sink.
